description._content: Page 9 of The D.H.S. Pointer, a publication of Deseronto High School, published by The Deseronto News Co. Ltd. in Deseronto, Ontario, at Easter 1920. This page lists "Our Fallen Heroes" "The following is a list of those who made the SUPREME SACRIFICE, and whose memory we desire especially to honour: FORMER STUDENTS OF THE D. H. S.
